headline: YETI Announces CFO Transition
summary: Seasoned Finance and Retail Industry Executive Scott Bomar Appointed Chief Financial Officer; Mike McMullen to Transition After Serving 10 Years at YETIAUSTIN, Texas, Feb. 19, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- YETI Holdings, Inc.
